header.name: Underwater Maze of the Spider Emperor
header.author: BSP-Dungeon-Generator
header.description: The maze of the Spider Emperor is situated deep in the frozen lands, in uncharted lands. Recently a band of thugs rediscovered it, making it their center of operation.

game_elements.name: Item 1
game_elements.description: A mouth-shaped wooden door on the northern wall of the small room.

game_elements.name: Item 2
game_elements.description: A corpse of a gnome, some gold close by.

game_elements.name: Item 3
game_elements.description: An ooze-covered body of a human, a vorpal long sword and a scale mail close to it.
